## Connected TV Workflow

- [ ] 1. Define objectives: Brand awareness, consideration, or direct response
- [ ] 2. Select CTV platforms: YouTube TV, Hulu, Roku, Peacock, etc.
- [ ] 3. Define audience: Device-based, behavioral, or contextual targeting
- [ ] 4. Choose ad format: Pre-roll, mid-roll, interactive, pause ads
- [ ] 5. Allocate budget: CPM vs. CPA goals, frequency targets
- [ ] 6. Creative specs: Match creative to CTV format requirements
- [ ] 7. Optimize: Adjust based on completion rates, VTR, and conversions

## Key Inputs
- Campaign objective: {{campaign_objective}}
- Target audience: {{target_audience}}
- Budget: {{budget}}
- Platforms: {{platforms}}
- Creative assets: {{creative_assets}}
